    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban councils considering PIP/DLA as income for council tax reduction schemes",
        "additional_details": "I don't think this should count has income for tax reduction schemes as personal independence payment/DLA is a Non-means-tested benefit and not taxable. I don't believe it is fair to count this as income when this money is used by a lot of disabled people for their disability needs.",
